            <title>[FLINK-1479] The spawned threads in the sorter have no context class loader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1479</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The context class loader of task threads is the user code class loader that has access to the libraries of the user program.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sorter spawns extra threads (reading, sorting, spilling) without setting the context class loader on those threads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
